<p> Watermelons typically take around 70-100 days to grow. Some smaller varieties of watermelon will grow faster, while larger varieties can take much longer</p> 
</div> 
<div class="section">
<p> Growing a watermelons is a long process that has several steps.<span class="highlight">These are three main steps to growing a watermelon.</span></p>
</div> 
<ol>
  <li>Plant watermelon seeds 1 inch deep in soil, preferably in mounds</li>
  <li>Water 1/2 inches every week</li>
  <li>Harvest when the belly of the watermelon turns yellow</li>
</ol> 
